28\'48om niet. Ich \u250\'fazemia sa vr\u225\'e1tili k p\u244\'f4vodn\u253\'fdm men\u225\'e1m \u352\'60ancov\u225\'e1, \u352\'60pit\u225\'e1lska, Gr\u246\'f6sslingova. Prinavr\u225\'e1tili sme si do ul\u237\'edc star\u353\'61iu hist\u243\'f3riu, ktorej v meste predt\u253\'fdm akoby ani nesmelo by\u357\'65, a dali sme si z\u225\'e1le\u382\'7ea\u357\'65.}
