\'edt na\u353\'61ich spolun\u225\'e1rodn\u253\'fdch pr\u237\'edslu\u353\'61n\u237\'edkov \u382\'7eij\u250\'facich za morom, \u382\'7ee to bolo dielo dlhoro\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9ho a \u382\'7eivot nasadzuj\u250\'faceho z\u225\'e1pasu legion\u225\'e1rov \u268\'0cechov a Slov\u225\'e1kov, \u382\'7ee to nebol len \u269\'0desk\u253\'fd sviatok, ktor\u253\'fd zabezpe\u269\'0dil pra\u382\'7esk\u253\'fd N\u225\'e1rodn\u253\'fd v\u253\'fdbor. }
